<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.3.6">
<l>vēṅkaṭaṅ kaṇmey mēlviṉai muṟṟavun</l>
<l>tāṅkaṭ ṭaṅkaṭku nallaṉavē ceyvār</l>
<l>vēṅka ṭattuṟai vārkku namaveṉṉa</l>
<l>lāṅkaṭa maiyatu cumantār kaṭkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Burning sins, even though the former karma of the body is finished,</l>
<l>they will make them good for themselves.</l>
<l>Paying obeissance to those who stay in Vēṅkaṭam</l>
<l>that is the duty of those who are burdened.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
